  "prompt": "What is the best answer I can give my girl when she asks me how are you?",
  "response": "When your girl asks you how you are, a thoughtful and engaging response can help strengthen your connection. Consider sharing something that reflects your feelings and invites further conversation. Here are a few options:\n\n1. **Positive and Honest**: \"I'm great, thanks! Just thinking about how lucky I am to have you in my life. How about you?\"\n  \n2. **Playful**: \"I'm doing well, but I could be even better if I had you by my side! How's your day going?\"\n\n3. **Reflective**: \"I\u2019ve been feeling a mix of things, but overall pretty good. I was just thinking about our last adventure together. How are you doing?\"\n\n4. **Genuine**: \"I\u2019m okay, just taking things one day at a time. How about you? What\u2019s been on your mind?\"\n\nChoose a response that matches your personality and the nature of your relationship!",
